# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __and__, __or__, __xor__ across all 6 decimal subjects
#
# 6 classes x 3 methods = 18 rows.
# All values are false: Decimal supports arithmetic but not bitwise operators;
# bitwise AND, OR, and XOR are integer operations not part of the IEEE 754
# decimal floating-point protocol. Context and exception subclasses likewise
# define no bitwise operators in their own __dict__.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

